{"tid":1932993,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"工會高層：整個NBA應有一半感染武漢肺炎","createTime":"2020-03-19T04:56:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T06:58:01.000Z","uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3ac89872810112852caaa2a9831d1beeb22a186e","tid":1932993,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T04:56:47.000Z","msg":"NBA確診武漢肺炎（COVID-19、新冠肺炎）球員數量昨（18）日從3例一夕暴增到7例，已經令球迷相當震驚，不過NBPA（美國國家籃球協會球員工會）執行理事Michele Roberts今語出驚人，表示全NBA包含工作人員應有一半人受感染。<br />\n<br />\n「我們之中將會很多人被測出陽性反應。即使尚未全面接受測試，我們仍帶原著病毒。我不打算點名，因為會害他們名譽受損。但是據我了解，接下來將會有更多NBA球員、員工、甚至是工會員工被確診。」Roberts受訪時告訴《USA Today體育》。<br />\n<br />\nRoberts語出驚人表示：「我聽到的數字是40%到50%，不管我們有沒有去做測試，真實的情況是，在整個NBA產業鏈當中有多達40%到50%將會被確診帶原武漢病毒。」<br />\n<br />\n目前確診武漢肺炎的NBA球員有Rudy Gobert（猶他爵士）、Donovan Mitchell（猶他爵士）、Christian Wood（底特律活塞）、Kevin Durant（布魯克林籃網）以及3名未公開的籃網球員，一共7人，相信球迷們也都不希望再見到此數字增加。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=710446\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D710446&d=AthmRk%2BBSDjaWf6zT95BzDcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=70c29df9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D710446&h=483cf6b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=710446</a>"},{"pid":"16ca9bef4dc6ff3b5359fd541566a2390f4f9ec5","tid":1932993,"uid":10290,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T05:08:07.000Z","msg":"唉要轉睇CBA"},{"pid":"a67c17a5275a6e460525677e775addd4891fd3b3","tid":1932993,"uid":6070,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"16ca9bef4dc6ff3b5359fd541566a2390f4f9ec5","tid":1932993,"uid":10290,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T05:08:07.000Z","msg":"唉要轉睇CBA"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T05:32:04.000Z","msg":"你有咩所謂 力羊都無人要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dec57d6d814fcdaa44a6f18d5634f9df085359cc","tid":1932993,"uid":10290,"like":